## Output Format

Return ONLY a valid JSON array. No markdown fences, no explanation outside the JSON.

```
[
  {
    "title": "Short descriptive title (10-15 words)",
    "novelty_argument": "Why this has NOT been done before — cite specific gaps from the corpus (2-3 sentences)",
    "methodology_hint": "Concrete methodological approach: what technique, dataset, or experimental design to use (2-3 sentences)",
    "difficulty": "easy|medium|hard",
    "expected_impact": "low|medium|high"
  }
]
```

Difficulty guide: easy = incremental extension of existing work, medium = new combination of known methods, hard = requires new theory or large-scale data collection.
Impact guide: low = niche contribution, medium = advances the subfield, high = paradigm shift or broad applicability.

Return ONLY the JSON array. No other text.
